Package com.ibm.avatar.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Chunker
    Interface for a callback that divides large documents into smaller chunks for processing.
    CompilationSummary
    This class contains the summary of AQL compilation process.
    ExternalTypeInfo
    An instance of this type acts as a container to hold information about external dictionaries and external tables.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AQLProfiler
    Utility class for profiling a modular extractor.
    AQLProfiler.RuntimeRecord  
    CompileAQL
    This class provides APIs to compile both modular and non-modular AQL files.
    CompileAQLParams
    This class encapsulates all parameters needed for compiling modular and non-modular AQL.
    DocReader
    This class provides APIs to read data from supported document collections.
    EmailChunker
    Document chunker for email messages.
    ExplainModule
    Describes the contents of a given compiled module in a human-readable format, which includes the module metadata, and the operator graph.
    ExternalTypeInfoFactory
    Factory class to create an ExternalTypeInfo instance.
    OperatorGraph
    This class provides APIs to load an operator graph from one or more compiled AQL modules; it also provides an API for extracting information using the loaded operator graph.
